"        logging expenses, generating spending summaries, and "
"personalizing\n"
"        your experience. We do not sell your personal data to third\n"
"        parties."
msgstr ""

#: templates/privacy.html:26
msgid "Data Storage"
msgstr ""

#: templates/privacy.html:28
msgid ""
